1. *Lažeš* mi (You are lying to me).
2. *Lažeš* da si srećan (You are lying that you are happy).
3. On *lažeš* da je ona kriva (He is lying that she is guilty).
4. Ono što *lažeš* je neistina (What you are lying is not true).
5. Čini se da *lažeš* (It looks like you are lying).
6. Zašto *lažeš*? (Why are you lying?)